# Ripgrep config
# See https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep/blob/master/GUIDE.md#configuration-file

# Don't let ripgrep vomit really long lines
--max-columns=150

# Search files that begin with a .
--hidden

# ...but not inside .git directories or mac clutter
--glob=!.git/*
--glob="!.DS_Store"

# pretty
# --pretty
--heading
--color=always
--line-number
--trim
--smart-case